## Bug Report

**What version of Rust are you using?**

```
$ rustc -V
rustc 1.32.0-nightly (14997d56a 2018-12-05)
```

**What did you do?**
```diff
$ rustfmt src/raftstore/store/fsm/store.rs
$ git diff
diff --git a/src/raftstore/store/fsm/store.rs b/src/raftstore/store/fsm/store.rs
index b5116fef..8a3f3c26 100644
--- a/src/raftstore/store/fsm/store.rs
