$ cargo build
error[E0659]: `rocksdb` is ambiguous (name vs any other name during import resolution)
  --> src/raftstore/store/fsm/store.rs:24:5
   |
24 | use rocksdb::{CompactionJobInfo, WriteBatch, WriteOptions, DB};
   |     ^^^^^^^ ambiguous name
   |
note: `rocksdb` could refer to the module imported here
  --> src/raftstore/store/fsm/store.rs:47:37
   |
47 | use crate::util::{is_zero_duration, rocksdb, sys as util_sys, Either, RingQueue};
   |                                     ^^^^^^^
   = help: use `self::rocksdb` to refer to this module unambiguously
note: `rocksdb` could also refer to the extern crate imported here
  --> src/lib.rs:74:1
   |
74 | extern crate rocksdb;
   | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
   = help: use `::rocksdb` to refer to this extern crate unambiguously
